						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Vijayanagarar Ariyana-Uḍaiyār, Dundubhi = 1382, Dec 27.</hi></p>						

						<p>Refers to a quarrel <hi rend="italic">(chiliku)</hi> between the right and left and castes which lasted for four, Years and consequent desertion of the temple streets. To encourage resettlement, tax concession was offered to the new settlers.</p>						

