<lb n="4"/><unclear>ka</unclear>varipiṇā poṟkoyil kaikkoḷaṟakku Aṟu<unclear>ti</unclear> paṇṇikkuṭutta
<lb n="5" break="no"/><unclear>paṭi</unclear> Ivūr valaṅkai Iṭaṅkai cilukāynāluvaru<hi rend="grantha">ṣa</hi>m pāḻ<unclear>ki</unclear>ṭakkaiyil
<lb n="6"/><supplied reason="omitted">ku</supplied>ṭi Ēṟakkaṭavarkaḷ Ākavum kuṭi Ēṟi Iṭattu taṟikkaṭamaivācal paṇam
<lb n="7"/>Aiñcu paṇam koḷḷakkaṭavatu Ākavum paṭṭaṭai nāṇayattuku pattil
<lb n="8"/>Aiñcu māṉiyattu Āṇṭu Oṉṟukku taṟioṉṟukku Oru paṇam ko<unclear>ḷḷavum</unclear>
